      <title>继美国提议后，法国拟就俄罗斯资产达成七国集团协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/france-aims-for-g-7-deal-on-russian-assets-after-us-proposal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国政府支持美国利用冻结的俄罗斯资产为乌克兰谋取利益的提议，提高了本周七国集团财长会议达成协议的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/france-aims-for-g-7-deal-on-russian-assets-after-us-proposal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 13:33:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>彼得森研究所波森称美联储将于 2025 年加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-22/fed-will-hike-in-2025-peterson-institute-s-posen-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彼得森国际经济研究所所长亚当·波森预计，美国总统大选后将出现“不可持续的繁荣”，因此美联储将不得不开始加息。他在彭博电视台发表讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-22/fed-will-hike-in-2025-peterson-institute-s-posen-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 13:27:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Anglo 在拒绝 490 亿美元报价后与必和必拓展开谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/anglo-opens-talks-with-bhp-after-rejecting-third-proposal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英美资源集团 (Anglo American Plc) 在拒绝了价值 386 亿英镑（合 490 亿美元）的第三项提议后，同意与规模更大的竞争对手必和必拓集团进行谈判，这首次为十多年来最大的矿业交易打开了大门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/anglo-opens-talks-with-bhp-after-rejecting-third-proposal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 13:23:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉马斯瓦米入股并寻求会谈，BuzzFeed 股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/buzzfeed-shares-soar-as-vivek-ramaswamy-takes-stake-seeks-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[企业家、前美国总统候选人维韦克·拉马斯瓦米 (Vivek Ramaswamy) 报告持有这家在线媒体公司的股份并要求与董事会进行会谈后，BuzzFeed Inc. 股价周三早些时候飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/buzzfeed-shares-soar-as-vivek-ramaswamy-takes-stake-seeks-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 12:12:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香奈儿暗示将迎来更艰难的时期，奢侈品牌股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/luxury-stocks-fall-as-chanel-results-hint-at-tougher-times-ahead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香奈儿警告称，该行业将面临更加困难的时期，分析师表示，他们认为该独家品牌的利润率面临越来越大的压力，周三欧洲奢侈品股遭受重创。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/luxury-stocks-fall-as-chanel-results-hint-at-tougher-times-ahead</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 11:55:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
