      <title>诺沃大厦一周内发生第二次火灾，面临倒塌危险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/novo-nordisk-hit-by-fire-in-denmark-for-second-time-in-one-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[诺和诺德公司 (Novo Nordisk A/S) 位于丹麦的总部大楼起火，一栋办公楼面临倒塌的危险，距离该公司另一家丹麦工厂发生火灾不到一周。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/novo-nordisk-hit-by-fire-in-denmark-for-second-time-in-one-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 09:34:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
